<h1 itemprop=headline>SplatHex displays Damage Up for All Gear</h1>
<time itemprop=datePublished datetime=2022-06-09>09 June 2022</time>
<img itemprop=image src=thumb-1.avif alt="Screenshot of SplatHex">
<p>Watch out for this SplatHex bug! Even though octoglasses' main ability is last-ditch effort, SplatHex shows damage up as the main ability! <strong>This is purely a display bug</strong>, and all gears' main ability will always be correct in-game.
